{"tid":997543,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"美國與塔利班和談重大進展  傳已同意一年半內撤軍","createTime":"2019-01-27T09:03:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-27T09:20:20.000Z","uid":28765,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"9d48c8703dc6e946b49786227588e1138a2395cd","tid":997543,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:03:49.000Z","msg":"（路透喀布爾26日電）塔利班（Taliban）官員表示，美國談判人員今天同意一項和平協議草案，倘若順利簽署，外國部隊將在18個月內撤出阿富汗。美國對外最長戰爭可望就此結束。<br />\n<br />\n美國特使哈里札德（Zalmay Khalilzad）與塔利班代表在卡達舉行6天談判，根據塔利班消息人士提供路透社的草案內容，談判目標在結束長達17年多的戰爭。<br />\n<br />\n草案明訂，部隊將會在這項協定簽署後的18個月內撤離阿富汗。<br />\n<br />\n然而雙方並未發布聯合聲明，哈里札德稍後推文說，這項談判已獲「重大進展」，很快就會舉行進一步會談，他計劃前往阿富汗會見阿國政府官員。中央社（翻譯）<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%87%E5%A1%94%E5%88%A9%E7%8F%AD%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%87-%E5%82%B3%E5%B7%B2%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F-%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A%E5%85%A7%E6%92%A4%E8%BB%8D-055117336.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.yahoo.com%2F%25E7%25BE%258E%25E5%259C%258B%25E8%2588%2587%25E5%25A1%2594%25E5%2588%25A9%25E7%258F%25AD%25E5%2592%258C%25E8%25AB%2587-%25E5%2582%25B3%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E5%2590%258C%25E6%2584%258F-%25E5%25B9%25B4%25E5%258D%258A%25E5%2585%25A7%25E6%2592%25A4%25E8%25BB%258D-055117336.html&d=IaL90kcc6RX%2FizET26T3O5WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=05b405ca\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.yahoo.com/%E7%BE%8E%E5%9C%8B%E8%88%87%E5%A1%94%E5%88%A9%E7%8F%AD%E5%92%8C%E8%AB%87-%E5%82%B3%E5%B7%B2%E5%90%8C%E6%84%8F-%E5%B9%B4%E5%8D%8A%E5%85%A7%E6%92%A4%E8%BB%8D-055117336.html</a>"},{"pid":"954bab8f58d1384a8764bee0f0ab4b2a9384be2b","tid":997543,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:07:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"230135886365dba2cea0d2046fbc43b5b0f7fc53","tid":997543,"uid":40216,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"954bab8f58d1384a8764bee0f0ab4b2a9384be2b","tid":997543,"uid":29702,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-27T09:07:33.000Z",